data.description: Great location - needs TLC! Spacious 4 bedroom across from Lakepointe Park with playground and playfields. Open and flowing floorplan with cathedral ceiling entry. Gas fireplace for winter warmth. Heat pump, ceiling fans and A/C.  Large living room is open to the kitchen & dining and is the heart of the home. Head upstairs for 3 bedrooms and laundry. The expansive primary bedroom has adjoining bath complete w/ double sinks & walk-in closet. 4th bedroom on main could be office or den. 2 car garage & cute backyard with patio & fully fenced. Easy back road JBLM commute. Near golfing, parks, lakes, schools, I-5, and Amtrak.
